      "post_id" : 11377996,
      "comment_id" : 82531033,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "<code>0x803BB9FF</code> is larger than <code>Integer.MAX_VALUE</code> (<code>0x7FFFFFFF</code>), that is why <code>Integer.parseInt()</code> and <code>Integer.decode()</code> can&#39;t handle it.  Use <code>Long</code> instead."
